				"ctgy":"IMPORTANT",
				"content":"<p><strong>Customer Service business hours:</strong><br /> - April 27th (SAT) through 29th (MON): closed<br /> - April 30th (TUE) through May 2nd (THU): from 9:30 to 18:30<br /> - May 3rd (FRI) through 6th (MON): closed<br /> (Customer service will return on regular business hours from May 7th.)</p> <p><strong>Transfer requests and remittance:</strong><br /> - Deposits made after bank hours from April 26th (FRI) until April 29th (MON) will be processed on April 30th (TUE).<br /> - Deposits made after bank hours from May 2nd (THU) until May 6th (MON) will be processed on May 7th (TUE).</p> <p><strong>New subscriptions:</strong><br /> Customers may apply online during the Golden Week holidays. The starter kit may take longer to be delivered due to the holiday hours.</p> <p>Thank you for your understanding.</p> <br /> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gocomments/brastelremit04.wordpress.com/223/\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/comments/brastelremit04.wordpress.com/223/\" /></a> <img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://stats.wordpress.com/b.gif?host=brastelremit04.wordpress.com&#038;blog=33283832&#038;post=223&#038;subd=brastelremit04&#038;ref=&#038;feed=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" />"
