				"content":"<p>Due to the end of year holidays, the business hours as well as the delivery date at the recipient countries may be effected.<br /> We recommend you to check with the local bank/financial institution beforehand to avoid unexpected delivery delays.</p> <br /> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gocomments/brastelremit04.wordpress.com/162/\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/comments/brastelremit04.wordpress.com/162/\" /></a> <img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://stats.wordpress.com/b.gif?host=brastelremit04.wordpress.com&#038;blog=33283832&#038;post=162&#038;subd=brastelremit04&#038;ref=&#038;feed=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" />"
