				"feed_href":"http://brastelremit04.wordpress.com/2012/12/18/brastel-remit-service-end-of-year-hours/",
				"ctgy":"IMPORTANT",
				"content":"<p>Due to the end of year holidays, Brastel Remit customer service and transaction hours will be as follows.</p> <p><strong>Customer service:</strong><br /> Customer service will be closed on December 22nd, December 29th to January 3rd, and January 5th.<br /> (Regular hours between December 25th and 28th and on January 4th.)</p> <p><strong>Transactions:</strong><br /> All deposits placed between December 28th and January 3rd out of bank business hours will be processed on January 4th.</p> <p><strong>Membership registrations:</strong><br /> Although the registration is available online throughout the year there will be a delay to receive the starter kit during the end of year holidays.</p> <p>Thank you for your understanding.</p> <br /> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gocomments/brastelremit04.wordpress.com/158/\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/comments/brastelremit04.wordpress.com/158/\" /></a> <img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://stats.wordpress.com/b.gif?host=brastelremit04.wordpress.com&#038;blog=33283832&#038;post=158&#038;subd=brastelremit04&#038;ref=&#038;feed=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" />"
