				"ctgy":"NEWS",
				"content":"<p>We are happy to inform you that Brastel Remit offers remittance service to the Philippines with two delivery methods for your convenience: Bank Transfer and Agent Collect Point.</p> <p>In the case of the Agent Collect Point method, <strong><i>Cebuana Lhuillier</i></strong> and <strong><i>M Lhuillier </i></strong>are the available agents.</p> <p>With bank and agent branches located in most areas of the country, sending money to your dear ones in the Philippines became easier and more convenient!</p> <p>For more information, please <a title=\"CONTACT US\" href=\"http://brastelremit.jp/eng/inquiry\" target=\"_blank\">contact our Customer Service</a>.</p> <br /> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gocomments/brastelremit04.wordpress.com/143/\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/comments/brastelremit04.wordpress.com/143/\" /></a> <img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://stats.wordpress.com/b.gif?host=brastelremit04.wordpress.com&#038;blog=33283832&#038;post=143&#038;subd=brastelremit04&#038;ref=&#038;feed=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" />"
